summary: The Female Housecarl\'s with a feminine stance and walk wearing the Tavern girl\'s outfit
descriptionHtml:
This is a modification of Sugaki\'s mod (found here: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3788# )

That puts the female housecarl\'s in tavern girl clothing so you can equip any armor you want, while giving them a more feminine stance and walk.

Thanks for all your work getting their stance and walk fixed Sudaki!! I love your mod!
author: Syeeb
